INSERT INTO scripts (stage, category, target_audience, script_role, tags, versions, sort_order)
VALUES (
  'Telemarketer — Qualified Leads CPF Angle (Golden Year Partners)',
  'cold-calling',
  'pre-retiree',
  'telemarketer',
  ARRAY['qualified-lead', 'cold-call', 'cpf', 'passive-income', 'retirement', 'text-message', 'pdf-guide'],
  '[{"author": "Template", "content": "Hi, is this (name) speaking?\n\nHi (name), this is just (your name) calling from Golden Year Partners.\n\nI''m the admin assistant for our retirement specialists.\n\nI saw you indicated interest in our retirement planning & CPF resources a while back via our online ads, just want to check if you''re looking out for information with regards to retirement planning?\n\n**(yes)** → proceed to next\n\n**(no)** I see, may I check if you''re past the age of 55 years old?\n\nDoesn''t matter if yes or no → I see, how is your retirement planning journey going so far? (chit chat)\n\nActually many of our readers who (same profile as the prospect) have found our resources and sessions to be quite useful to help them better plan towards their retirement, if you don''t mind I can share with you a bit more?\n\n---\n\n### Two Common Categories\n\nUsually people who request for our resources, they usually fall into one of these two categories. Maybe I''ll just share them with you, see if you resonate with any of them:\n\n1. **CPF SA Closing** — With CPF SA account will be closing next year for those 55 and above, and they are wondering if there are better ways to grow their money above the 2.5% p.a. in OA\n\n2. **ERS Increasing** — With ERS increasing to 4X of BRS next year, some are considering if it''s worth doing the top up, or if there are better options out there, so they want to make a more informed decision.\n\nWould you say any of these resonate with you?\n\n(first, second, or whatever reason they share, chit chat with them)\n\n---\n\n### For leads within 2 months:\n\nThat''s great (name), usually for most of our readers who share this concern, what I''d recommend is for me to arrange a short 30 minute zoom session for one of my retirement specialists to share with you more about possible options which you can explore, to help you plan towards a better retirement.\n\nWould you prefer weekdays or weekends?\n\n(proceed to set appointment)\n\n---\n\n### For leads more than 2 months:\n\nThat''s great (name), as recently there have been some changes in the retirement planning landscape and we want to make sure you guys get the latest information. So what we''ve come up with is a short PDF guide based on the recent CPF changes and how you can best plan towards your retirement. Would you like me to drop you a copy via WhatsApp later?\n\n**(okay sure / yes)**\n\nGreat, I will send it to you right after we end this call. This guide will definitely be useful based on what you''ve shared with me. However, it may not help you to get full clarity on your retirement. We do have clients in the similar situation being able to achieve their retirement goals, or even having more than what they''re planning for.\n\nRegardless if you''re interested in becoming our clients, what our consultants can share with you is what are some of the frameworks and methods our clients are using to help them achieve an additional $1,000 to $2,000/month in passive income, would that be something you''d be open to?\n\n(proceed to set appointment)\n\n---\n\n### Once appointment set:\n\nOkay so what''s gonna happen next is I will be sending you a confirmation text and a brief agenda of what we will be running through during the session so you can have a clear idea of what to expect. I will also send you a reminder one day before the allocated time slot. Do me a favour and help me acknowledge the text, is that okay?\n\n---\n\n## 📌 Calling Tips\n\n- **Take note** the calling script only serves as a guide. When it comes to calling, a lot of it comes to how you interact with the respective leads.\n\n- **Be friendly and cheerful** in your tonality. The more likeable you are, the more people are willing to chat.\n\n- **Sell the value of appointment and the retirement specialists** — e.g. \"Many people who have scheduled a consultation session with us have found it to be very useful, as our retirement specialists focus on creating a tailored strategy that will really benefit you and help you work towards your ideal retirement.\"\n\n- **Prompt responses** — When the leads come in during daytime (9am to 6pm), contact them within a 20 minute window, so they remember that they have opted in for something."}]'::jsonb,
  25
);